| Scenario                           | Best Choice      |
| ---------------------------------- | ---------------- |
| Find only 2nd highest              | MAX subquery     |
| Top N rankings                     | DENSE_RANK       |
| Partitioned rankings               | Window functions |
| Reporting analytics                | Window functions |
| Performance-critical simple lookup | MAX              |



 
 
 
